sentences: Mario TomiÄ‡ (born 1987, Split) is a Croatian music arranger, composer, jazz musician, guitarist and music producer.
Label Guitar Records named him world's best guitarist of 2005.
In 2012 he received Silver award for jazz-fusion composition of the year given by Uplay for his composition "Tribual fusion".
